The Ten Tigers from Kwangtung attempt to protect a revolutionary from the Manchu government, but their actions have fatal consequences for their disciples.
 The Shaw Brothers' greatest stars have assembled here to take on this legendary tale. The cast includes Ti Lung (Drunken Master 2, The Deadly Duo), Alexander Fu Sheng (Heroes Two, The Brave Archer), Wang Lung Wei (The Master), Philip Kwok (The Flag of Iron) and a veritable who's who of kung fu film legends.
 This classic film from 1979 was directed by the influential Chang Cheh (Five Element Ninjas).
